description.en-us: Octopus MAX EZ, a 32 bit motherboard, is an upgraded version of Octopus Pro
description.zh-cn: Octopus MAX EZ是一款32位主板，是Octopus Pro的升级版本。

description.en-us: BIGTREETECH Octopus-pro V1.0 is a powerful and feature rich, 3D printer motherboard that supports up to 8 60V stepper drivers
description.zh-cn: BIGTREETECH Octopus-pro V1.0是一款功能强大且特性丰富的3D打印机主板，支持多达8个60V步进电机驱动器。
